para_trans: 30 bed capacity rural primary health centre at Buldhana
Government Decision, No: Grades-2024 / Q.69 / Health 3
Read: Letter from the Commissionerate of Health Services, Mumbai by No. / Room3 / T-2 / No.
Udaynagar (Undri), Ta. A proposal to upgrade the Primary Health Centre at Chikhali, District Buldhana to a 30-bed rural hospital was under consideration of the Government.
Udaynagar (Undri), Ta. Primary Health Centre at Chikhli, District Buldhana with 30 bed capacity

Grading in rural hospitals is being approved as a "special case" under this government decision. Construction and creation of posts by acquisition of land for this upgraded hospital in the prescribed manner.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
